while true do
    -- Suck items from the chest above
    while turtle.suckUp() do
        -- Get item details including damage
        local item_detail = turtle.getItemDetail(1, true)
        
        if item_detail then
            -- Check if item is a potion
            local is_potion = string.find(item_detail.name, "potion$")

            if is_potion then
                print("Potion detected: " .. item_detail.name)
                -- Drop potions down
                turtle.dropDown()

            elseif item_detail.damage and item_detail.maxDamage then
                -- Check if the item is damaged
                if item_detail.damage < item_detail.maxDamage then
                    print("Item is damaged: " .. item_detail.name .. " | Damage: " .. item_detail.damage .. "/" .. item_detail.maxDamage)
                    -- Drop the damaged item down
                    turtle.dropDown()
                else
                    -- Push the item to the front chest
                    turtle.drop()
                end
            else
                -- If no damage information, push the item to the front chest
                turtle.drop()
            end
        else
            -- Fallback if item details can't be read
            turtle.drop()
        end
    end
    
    sleep(5) -- Sleep for 5 seconds before checking again
end
